textBox.richText: Woke up to a little more snow than expected. The weather report said 1-15degF, so Alli and Max decided to stay home. I dropped some CH6 on the S7s, and convinced Günter to come out early. Some places were “dust on crust”, but the HiLo trees were pretty good. They opened up Cheshire Cat (yay!), and we caught rope drops on Phantom Bridge and Bradley’s Bash.
